trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueue.ReceiveCompleted"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Messaging.MessageQueue.ReceiveCompleted"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: When your asynchronous receive operation calls an event handler, an instance of this class is passed to the handler.
trans-unit.target: Den asynkrone mottar operasjonen kaller hendelsesbehandling, en forekomst av denne klassen er sendt til et behandlingsprogram.

trans-unit.source: When you use event notification to receive messages asynchronously from the queue, you must create a method that handles your message processing.
trans-unit.target: Når du bruker hendelsesvarsling for å motta meldinger asynkront fra køen, må du opprette en metode som behandler meldingsbehandling.

trans-unit.source: Your code must call <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A> to begin the asynchronous processing.
trans-unit.target: Koden må kalle <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A>starter asynkron behandling.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A>

trans-unit.source: When a message is received, your application is notified through the <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.ReceiveCompleted> event.
trans-unit.target: Når en melding er mottatt programmet varslet via den <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.ReceiveCompleted>hendelsen.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.ReceiveCompleted>

trans-unit.source: An instance of ReceiveCompletedEventArgs is passed into the event delegate that calls your event handler.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av ReceiveCompletedEventArgs er sendt til denne hendelsen representanten som kaller hendelsesbehandlingen.

trans-unit.source: The data associated with the <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.ReceiveCompleted> event is contained in the delegate's <xref:System.Messaging.ReceiveCompletedEventArgs.AsyncResult%2A> parameter.
trans-unit.target: Data som er tilknyttet den <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.ReceiveCompleted>hendelsen ligger i representanten <xref:System.Messaging.ReceiveCompletedEventArgs.AsyncResult%2A>parameteren.</xref:System.Messaging.ReceiveCompletedEventArgs.AsyncResult%2A> </xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.ReceiveCompleted>

trans-unit.source: There are two ways to provide notification of event completion: event notification and callbacks.
trans-unit.target: Det er to måter å varsle hendelsen fullført: hendelsesvarsling og tilbakeringinger.

trans-unit.source: ReceiveCompletedEventArgs is used only with event notification.
trans-unit.target: ReceiveCompletedEventArgs brukes bare med hendelsesvarsling.

trans-unit.source: For information comparing callbacks and event notification, see "Events vs. Callbacks" on MSDN.
trans-unit.target: Du finner informasjon sammenligne tilbakeringinger og hendelsesvarsling i "hendelser i forhold til Tilbakeringinger"på MSDN.

trans-unit.source: ReceiveCompletedEventArgs provides access to the message that initiated the end of the asynchronous receive operation, through the <xref:System.Messaging.ReceiveCompletedEventArgs.Message%2A> member.
trans-unit.target: ReceiveCompletedEventArgs gir tilgang på meldingen som startet på slutten av den asynkrone motta operasjonen via den <xref:System.Messaging.ReceiveCompletedEventArgs.Message%2A>medlem.</xref:System.Messaging.ReceiveCompletedEventArgs.Message%2A>

trans-unit.source: This is an alternate access to the message, and behaves much the same as a call to <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en alternativ tilgang til meldingen, og fungerer mye lik et kall til <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the result of the asynchronous operation requested.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir resultatet av den asynkrone operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: AsyncResult identifies ongoing or completed asynchronous operations.
trans-unit.target: AsyncResult identifiserer pågående eller fullført asynkrone operasjoner.

trans-unit.source: The property contains data that helps determine which of several potential asynchronous operations to complete, and when passed to the event handler, enables <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A> to access the message associated with the completed operation.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen inneholder data som hjelper deg å fastslå hvilke av flere potensielle asynkrone operasjoner fullført, og når sendt til hendelsesbehandlingen aktiverer <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A>å åpne meldingen for fullførte operasjonen.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you call <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A>, a <xref:System.IAsyncResult> is returned immediately, even though a message, if one exists, has not yet been retrieved because the operation is not completed.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A>, en <xref:System.IAsyncResult>returneres umiddelbart, selv om en melding, hvis det finnes ikke ennå er hentet fordi operasjonen ikke er fullført.</xref:System.IAsyncResult> </xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A>

trans-unit.source: The AsyncResult indicates the state of the asynchronous operation.
trans-unit.target: AsyncResult angir tilstanden til den asynkrone operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A> creates the object, which is modified throughout the operation until <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A> completes it.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A>oppretter objektet, som er endret i operasjonen før <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A>er fullført det.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A></xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.BeginReceive%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.IAsyncResult> that contains the data associated with the receive operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IAsyncResult>som inneholder data som er knyttet til receive-operasjonen.</xref:System.IAsyncResult>

trans-unit.source: Gets the message associated with the asynchronous receive operation.
trans-unit.target: Henter meldingen som er tilknyttet den asynkrone motta operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The Message property provides a means for retrieving the message that initiated the end of the asynchronous receive operation.
trans-unit.target: Meldingsegenskapen inneholder en metode for å hente meldingen som startet på slutten av den asynkrone motta operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is called the first time the Message property is read, so it is not necessary to call <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A> prior to getting the value of this property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A?displayProperty=fullName>kalles første gang meldingsegenskapen leses, slik det ikke er nødvendig å kalle <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A>før henting av verdien for denne egenskapen.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A></xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue.EndReceive%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Messaging.Message"></xref> that represents the end result of the asynchronous receive operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Messaging.Message"> </xref> som representerer slutten motta resultatet av den asynkrone operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The Message could not be retrieved.
trans-unit.target: Meldingen kunne ikke hentes.

trans-unit.source: The time-out on the asynchronous operation might have expired.
trans-unit.target: Tidsavbrudd på den asynkrone operasjonen kan være utgått.
